name: Alice Yeboah
description: I am a young woman with strong belief there is an existence of love and for my life on this,i will love been a good woman and a perfect wife for my man,i am very passionate and treat people of all ages and all walks of life with respect,i also believe that the happiness of every woman is based on a loving Husband to fulfill the pleasures and desires of her,i enjoy going out with friends and i do enjoy going to the movies and also enjoy reading books that are very much adventurous,i am very honest and sincere and believes it is good thing to be kind and faithful in life.I want a man with a sweet loving and kind heart that is ready for a relationship that is ready to be taken up and to live to expectation,i want a serious man and hardworking as well that is very much respectful to women and is ready to start a relationship with me..
